在分子生物學中，'''5.8S核糖體RNA'''（'''5.8S rRNA''')是指一類[[非編碼RNA|非編碼RNA]]。它是真核生物[[核糖體|核糖體]]的大亞基的組成成分，在[[翻译_(遗传学)|蛋白質轉譯]]中起重要作用。{{link-en|RNA聚合酶I|RNA polymerase I}}先[[轉錄|轉錄]]出[[沉降係數|沉降係數]]爲45S的前體。該前體同樣包含[[18S_rRNA|18S rRNA]]和[[28S_rRNA|28S rRNA]]。5.8S rRNA在核糖體轉運中起作用<ref name=Abou_1997>{{cite journal | last = Abou | first = Elela S |author2= Nazar RN | year = 1997 | title = Role of the 5.8S rRNA in ribosome translocation | journal = Nucleic Acids Res | volume = 25 | pages = 1788–1794 | pmid = 9108162 | doi = 10.1093/nar/25.9.1788 | issue = 9 | pmc = 146658}}</ref>。它能夠和[[p53|p53]]腫瘤抑制蛋白形成[[共價|共價]]連接<ref name=Fontoura_197>{{cite journal | last = Fontoura | first = BM |author2=Atienza CA|author3=Sorokina EA|author4=Morimoto T|author5= Carroll RB | year = 1997 | title = Cytoplasmic p53 polypeptide is associated with ribosomes | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_1997-06_17_6/page/3146 | journal = Mol Cell Biol | volume = 17 | pages = 3146–3154 | pmid = 9154813 | issue = 6 | pmc = 232167}}</ref>。

5.8S rRNA可以作爲[[RT-PCR|RT-PCR]]检测[[miRNA|miRNA]]表达量的内参基因<ref name="s58_real">{{cite journal |author=Shi R, Chiang VL |title=Facile means for quantifying microRNA expression by real-time PCR |journal=BioTechniques |volume=39 |issue=4 |pages=519–25 |date=October 2005 |pmid=16235564 |doi=10.2144/000112010 |url=http://www.biotechniques.com/article/000112010 |accessdate=2010-09-15 |archive-date=2012-07-31 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120731010516/http://www.biotechniques.com/article/000112010 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

